      <title>生产率低于平均水平的英国公司雇佣了 70% 的员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/uk-firms-with-below-average-productivity-employ-70-of-workers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国创造和破坏的就业岗位数量大幅下降，而顶级企业对市场的控制力也不断收紧，这是英国经济陷入长期停滞的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/uk-firms-with-below-average-productivity-employ-70-of-workers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 11:30:37 GMT</pubDate>
